858
01:17:34,944 --> 01:17:36,780
Prioritas? Pernah
dengar istilah triase?

859
01:17:36,863 --> 01:17:39,115
- Dia akan mati sebelum turun.
- Kau tak tahu itu!

860
01:17:40,784 --> 01:17:42,494
