Ayo! Ayo, Ghoul! Masuk
ke lubang. Diam di sana!

889
01:20:18,387 --> 01:20:21,515
Ayo, Smitty, kami akan
melindungimu! Maju!

890
01:20:28,021 --> 01:20:29,189
Lindungi.

891
01:20:36,362 --> 01:20:37,905
Satchel!

892
