Lindungi dia.

897
01:21:23,572 --> 01:21:26,242
Medis! Tolong aku!

898
01:21:53,933 --> 01:21:54,767
Ayo!

899
01:22:38,725 --> 01:22:40,143
Tolong! Medis!

900
01:22:44,022 --> 01:22:47,566
Aku di sini. Letakkan
tanganmu di atasnya!

