01:39:07,637 --> 01:39:09,514
Enam... Delapan...

1021
01:39:10,807 --> 01:39:13,643
- Empat belas.
- Amankan mereka.

1022
01:39:13,726 --> 01:39:14,769
Ya, Pak.

1023
01:39:14,852 --> 01:39:18,814
- Prajurit Ford, berapa orang?
- Hanya 32 yang turun, Pak.

1024
01:39:19,773 --> 01:39:21,358
- Astaga.
- Ayo!

1025
01:39:22,985 --> 01:39:24,861
- Ayo bawa mereka.
- Ya, Pak.

1026
01:40:04,231 --> 01:40:07,900
Harry. Ini Desmond.
Kita akan mengobatimu.

1027
01:40:07,984 --> 01:40:09,944
Kau harus terus bernapas.

1028
01:40:11,362 --> 01:40:14,032
- Kolonel ingin menemuimu.
- Aku butuh jipmu.

1029
01:40:14,115 --> 01:40:16,743
Kalian tetap di sini,
awasi tentara Jepang.

1030
01:40:16,826 --> 01:40:18,286
- Namun...
- Tetap di sini!

1031
01:40:18,369 --> 01:40:19,871
- Ya, Pak!
- Ya, Pak!

